## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **T-DXd Enhertu 2019 → 2022 HER2-low → 2024 HER2-ultralow → 2024 lung** = HER2 ADC paradigm shift. HER2-low (IHC 1+ or 2+/FISH-) classification 자체가 2022 DESTINY-Breast04 결과로 신설 — biomarker-driven indication expansion. quantum-VQE 의 HER2 ECD + DXd linker scaffold 직접 fit.
2. **capivasertib Truqap 2023** = first FDA AKT inhibitor — AKT1/PIK3CA/PTEN-altered HR+ HER2- metastatic breast (CAPItello-291). PI3K-AKT-mTOR axis 의 next node. quantum-VQE 의 AKT1 E17K mutated pocket leverage.
3. **inavolisib Itovebi 2024** = second PI3Kα selective + endocrine + palbociclib triplet — INAVO120 결과 PFS 두 배. alpelisib 부작용 (hyperglycemia + 발진) 개선. PI3Kα H1047R selectivity 개선.
4. **elacestrant Orserdu 2023** = first FDA oral SERD — ESR1-mutated HR+ HER2- metastatic 후-CDK4/6. fulvestrant IM 2002 후 21년 만에 oral alternative. ESR1 Y537S/D538G 임상적 의미.
5. **vepdegestrant ARV-471 2024 Phase 3 VERITAC-2** = first ER PROTAC clinical readout — ESR1m post-CDK4/6. cereblon-based ER ubiquitination + proteasomal degradation. SERD 와 mechanism 다름 (degradation vs antagonism). quantum-VQE 의 ternary complex 모델링 fit.
6. **olaparib OlympiA adjuvant 2022** = first PARP adjuvant in BRCA1/2-mutated HER2- early breast (high-risk post-neoadjuvant). adjuvant landscape 진입 — disease-modifying.
7. **palbociclib + ribociclib + abemaciclib 2015-2017** = HR+ HER2- 1L + 2L + adjuvant (abemaciclib 2021 monarchE) standard. CDK4/6 + AI 또는 + fulvestrant — endocrine alone 시대 종료.
8. **sacituzumab govitecan Trodelvy 2020 → 2023 HR+** = first FDA TROP2 ADC — TNBC ASCENT 후 HR+ TROPiCS-02. TROP2 broader expression — pan-breast modality.
9. **pembrolizumab KEYNOTE-355 + KEYNOTE-522 2020-2021** = TNBC 1L PD-L1 CPS≥10 + neoadjuvant pCR rate 향상. atezolizumab 2021 withdrawal 후 PD-1 mAb single dominant. TNBC IO single biomarker.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, breast cancer 임상 의미 한정.

